      "content": "Your perspective is heavy, but it is important to remember that the world is smaller than it feels when you are carrying that burden alone. While change might feel impossible right now, your feelings of exhaustion are signals that you need support rather than evidence that this is your permanent fate. Please consider talking to a therapist who specializes in existential burnout to help you find meaning even in a time when it feels hard to see.",
      "source": "target",
